name: Pray For Semeru
description:
100% of the proceeds from the sale of NFT will be donated to victims of the Mount Semeru eruption natural disaster through an organization/entity and will be announced on my social media twitter.

Let us pray that our brothers and sisters affected by the eruption of Mount Semeru in Lumajang and its surroundings will be given patience, strength, safety, and always in the protection of Allah SWT, Amen.
